me":"Hungarian","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar"},{"english_name":"Turkish","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe"}],"status":"Ended","tagline":"","type":"Scripted","vote_average":5.5,"vote_count":2}},"person_2509433_translations":{"at":1774376994130,"data":{"id":2509433,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"อาเชน ไอย์ดึน","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Joong Archen Aydin is a model, actor, singer and member of the actor-based project group JASP.ER under GMMTV and Riser Music. Born in Thailand, he moved to Türkiye at eight years old with his mother and stepfather and lived there until he was sixteen. Joong then came back to Thailand to finish his education. He changed his name a number of times before entering show business, including taking his stepfather's surname. He is currently studying broadcasting and streaming media production at Bangkok University's School of Communication Arts.\n\nHe made his acting debut in 2019 with a main role in the series \"2 Moons 2\".\n\nJoong was formerly a member of boy group \"OXQ\" under Motive Village and boy group \"Insight Rookies\" under Insight Entertainment. Joong has been an artist under GMMTV since September 2021. On December 19, 2024, he made his debut with Project JASP.ER with the release of their debut single \"Sadistic\".","name":"Archen Aydin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿晨·艾丁","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Joong Archen Aydin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"阿晨·艾丁","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Archen Aydin, conhecido mundialmente como Joong, é um ator, cantor e modelo tailandês sob o selo da GMMTV e Riser Music. Nascido na Tailândia como Rachen Lueangthong, Joong mudou-se para a Turquia aos oito anos, onde viveu por quase uma década, o que lhe conferiu fluência no idioma turco. Ele retornou à Tailândia aos 16 anos para seguir sua educação e carreira artística, estudando atualmente Produção de Mídia e Streaming na Universidade de Bangkok.\n\nSua estreia na atuação ocorreu em 2019 como protagonista na série \"2 Moons 2\". Após passagens pelos grupos musicais OXQ e Insight Rookies, Joong assinou com a GMMTV em 2021, alcançando o estrelato global ao formar a parceria JoongDunk na série \"Star and Sky: Star in My Mind\" (2022). Em 2024, ele estreou no grupo de performance JASP.ER com o single \"Sadistic\". Joong é reconhecido por sua versatilidade, transitando entre papéis em comédias românticas e projetos de ação como \"The Heart Killers\" (2024). Em 2025/2026, Joong desafiou as expectativas ao protagonizar a série de mistério \"Dare You To Death\", onde a sua performance mais sombria e intensa foi aclamada pela crítica.","name":"Joong Archen Aydin","primary":false}}]}},"tv_295483_credits":{"at":1774377001025,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1254300,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Mai Fuchigami","original_name":"渕上舞","popularity":1.3503,"profile_path":"/rWYdSVyjdyKoWj9SbJRTMJmYgbJ.jpg","character":"Tiararose (voice)","credit_id":"68913f1a24f18fded3b23473","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1483496,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Yuuichirou Umehara","original_name":"梅原裕一郎","popularity":2.7893,"profile_path":"/lScrvZi4tKKpk3PbnIjLVjHVNJn.jpg","character":"Aquasteed (voice)","credit_id":"68913f29825dd7dd12a46bcd","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1253431,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Takuya Sato","original_name":"佐藤拓也","popularity":1.4201,"profile_path":"/xZgoTs6DOSneHkoOWL751pQzLru.jpg","char